current.summary: Bike: Structured - Spin Ups (:30 sin ups)
current.description:
Workout type: Bike
Warm up. Then do 8 x spin ups. Spin up to a high cadence. When you start bouncing in your seat, back off and recover for 2 minutes. Then repeat. Don't push a big gear on the spin ups. This workout is to keep your legs sharp and increase cadence, not power.
Planned Time: 1:00
